reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Screen cracks very easily.
reviews.reviewText: This product is awful. I didn't really want to buy a two pack protector because I never crack it. I went ahead and bought it and within just a few weeks it had several scratches and cracks. I didn't even know what I did to cause them. I finally replaced about a week ago with the second one. Within days it has a huge crack all the way across it with no bad drop or anything that would have caused such a crack. I will not buy this product again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Love the privacy, shattered easily
reviews.reviewText: I really like the level of privacy I have while still being able to have my brightness at a decent level.There was a minor crack that happened during applying the screen on top of my screen. Over time that crack has started to flake and spread lines across the screen. So a little annoying how easily it broke just installing it… it is very delicate, but luckily there is a second screen I can put on once the current crack bothers me enough to change it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to apply and no bubbles!
reviews.reviewText: I got a different brand several days ago that came with two protectors/privacy screens (the kind that was had a rectangle taken out of the top in stead of a rectangle hole).This other brand….. I put the first one on after cleaning and there were bubbles. So I cleaned again and put the second one on and there were less bubbles but two small bubbles. I woke up the next day and the small bubbles had turned into a giant bubble and it messed up my keyboard, like it wouldn’t recognize typing pressure.So, thoroughly annoyed, I ordered this one as replacement (thinking the shape would make it better to apply). I was right! The first one of this one (came with two) went on better right away, super easy to apply. The privacy is great and no issues with keyboard pressure or bubbles. Very pleased!
It’s is good but breaks quite easily as I drop my phone most of the time. I just got a flip cover as I need 2-3 screen guards every month.
